^Help - Smail
USAGE: .smail ^user message
WHERE: ^user^ is an alias
       ^message^ is a message you wish them to get

Use this command when you want to leave a ^message^ to ^user^ that can be read
later.  This works even if ^user^ is offline.  If they are online, they will
be notified immediately that you have written them smail.

SEE ALSO
  ^.help rmail^, ^.help cmail
